{"tid":984140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"農民工提早「收爐」回鄉  官方：回鄉創業愈來愈吸引","createTime":"2019-01-16T14:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T10:04:38.000Z","uid":51183,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5dea2983ad852f5039e5870fac734fc1f249dd","tid":984140,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/2181634295445019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F2181634295445019%2F&d=RTsWOQJ2NVSqFPKyJPBKg8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=be470dd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/2181634295445019/</a><br />\n【農民工提早「收爐」回鄉】<br />\n【人社部：回鄉創業愈來愈吸引】<br />\n<br />\n即將踏入春運高峰期，不少民工陸續回鄉度歲，但今年似乎走得特別早。有地盤工人指工程提早完成，所以提早「收爐」。<br />\n<br />\n事實上去年內地製造業的寒冬來得更早，東莞有製衣廠指因應生產情況，早在去年12月1號已經開始放農曆新年假，直至3月上旬，長達約100日。另外，江蘇宜興亦有紡織廠指市場進入淡季提早停產，工人要提早放年假。<br />\n<br />\n人力資源社會保障部承認，去年12月提早回鄉的農民工比前年同期略增加，但認為總體就業數據保持穩定：「有的是因為家裡原因他要回去，有的是他家門口就業崗位增加了。另外農民工返鄉創業政策含金量愈來愈高，所以有一部分他是回去準備在家裡創業，或者在家門口就業。當然也有一些是受到企業生產經營下滑的影響。」<br />\n<br />\n他多次強調全國就業情況穩定，去年新增就業總數達到1361萬，比去年同期增加了10萬，市場上職位供應多過求職人數，失業率3.8%，是近年低位。<br />\n<br />\n人社部強調未來會有政策穩定企業經營環境，減少企業裁員，亦會幫助農民工在家鄉創業。<br />\n<br />\n不過經濟學者胡星斗指出「城鎮失業登記率」，不包括農民工，而絕大多數失業的人是不去登記的，所以官方數據失真，未有反映真實狀況。對於農民工回鄉創業的說法，胡星斗亦覺得是過於理想化，因為農村沒有創業的條件。<br />\n<br />\n#回鄉創業<br />\n#農民工提早返鄉<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國只有就業同創業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044d1d70e172d8da22ba0f8cd6d3e451fd1191de","tid":984140,"uid":152476,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"中國特色失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5e17c6a7fd97a9309da33bfb55bfba2783e5c7","tid":984140,"uid":220701,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>   他多次強調全國就業情況穩定，去年新增就業總數達到1361萬，比去年同期增加了10萬，市場上職位供應多過求職人數，失業率3.8%，是近年低位。 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d3cc63c9e956dfeb44f97b17c7a4c80728622e","tid":984140,"uid":38651,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"提早收爐定提早收皮呀?"},{"pid":"47f5d0311eeccec1a43c65fc5f58c55ee6eab406","tid":984140,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"趕晒回農村, 就唔計失業, 即是無失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516f6b38ec21eb8048b3f1ed961f2737cdbf5135","tid":984140,"uid":46631,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"在家門口就業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搶埋看門口隻汪財份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b062149906a5a94ace719a1ef69e5f1d3982ac","tid":984140,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"516f6b38ec21eb8048b3f1ed961f2737cdbf5135","tid":984140,"uid":46631,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"在家門口就業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搶埋看門口隻汪財份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee1311978e7a145faa2306f0300343a72827aae","tid":984140,"uid":166032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e359b06f161c9c16ce61caa9066335203eaf122a","tid":984140,"uid":46947,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"放